{"tid":401624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好憎自己嘅性格","createTime":"2017-09-15T17:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T20:45:02.000Z","uid":142375,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6580982e275864e500627cb2580b22c50c1df7","tid":401624,"uid":142375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:57:40.000Z","msg":"自己本身講野唔叻，亦冇乜自信<br />\n所以當一大班人聚會嗰陣，就算大部分都係熟嘅人都會唔敢出聲，驚會dead air<br />\n上ig見人成班fd玩會好葡萄，但身處係人群當中嗰陣又會怕、唔鍾意<br />\n好多時都會將自己放得好後，只要人地開心，我就下對方都冇所謂<br />\n但係就搞到自己變咗個冇主見嘅人<br />\n<br />\n拍拖方面，明明已經好努力咁付出<br />\n但總係做得唔夠，好似唔識對人好咁<br />\n我係個佔有慾好強嘅人，男朋友提一提起第二個女仔都會唔開心一陣<br />\n但係每次都會扮冇野，附和下話個女仔真係幾靚幾好喎等等<br />\n就係唔想男朋友發現自己呢一點<br />\n男朋友做錯野嗰陣會講好多說話希望佢經歷返差唔多程度嘅傷心，但第二日就會後悔，覺得自己好衰<br />\n<br />\n未必全部關性格事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之就成日都覺得自己好差，永遠都比唔上其他人<br />\n<br />\n利申，天蠍絲"},{"pid":"ccf77e5575d8fe71ea8dc20d1d46166eebbfc28e","tid":401624,"uid":137519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:06:59.000Z","msg":"實遇到一個會夾既"},{"pid":"56f0acbbb23094e2f46ebc49ac02e6f5945d0e45","tid":401624,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:07:03.000Z","msg":"我都覺得自己係辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9bc5c7c4e1f30f8bf04040e44fe14899c5aea7","tid":401624,"uid":46385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:20:37.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481588452a28b16996c7aa4edfa190a662caf313","tid":401624,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:21:12.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"d80684c40851599e19e6ab1847312c56b6c96086","tid":401624,"uid":120101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:22:19.000Z","msg":"我都係，預咗孤獨終老"},{"pid":"6b701955cc58a31305cba8dc589127d6e4b79421","tid":401624,"uid":133030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:25:52.000Z","msg":"頭嗰段根本係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />熟嘅朋友幾嘈都冇問題 一大班人我就即刻變社交障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得自己係由細到大俾屋企人嫌乜都做得唔夠好 所以搞到自己冇自信 好難改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0541b0fd82aa6e3a98840addcc92554a9abf9c0e","tid":401624,"uid":76723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:54:18.000Z","msg":"頭個段係難改啲 係大班人面前就唔好勉強喇 我有個fd都係咁 但私底下單獨個時完全相反 癲婆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後面個段同你一樣 唔想比男朋友知 但係個心又有啲un住un住咁 唔想比佢知我咁小既事都咁執著..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b752505cd05df84600b5e730dd34c3ef8e537b0","tid":401624,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68af6bbdfe8442bd7f19065e291e66f41f667501","tid":401624,"uid":109042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T19:59:06.000Z","msg":"同你80%相似，一樣係天蠍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9947f8f6225e28823d13fe3b552ede5b2758051","tid":401624,"uid":142462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T19:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3534b6337aee35a39c3122c835cec86303bdc7","tid":401624,"uid":142462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T20:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申天秤巴"},{"pid":"348c284c1d40ff61df936608c7070561911cd094","tid":401624,"uid":31733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T20